ilippa.cole@unimib.it\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">philippa.cole@unimib.it<\/a><br><em>Dark matter hunter, gravitational wave decipherer, primordial black hole dreamer. Looking for signatures of dark matter in gravitational wave signals. Enjoys food-centric trips around the world and dancing to Beyonce.<\/em><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns coblocks-author-columns has-background is-layout-flex wp-container-12 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"background-color:#8C8C971A;padding-top:2.5rem;padding-right:2.5rem;padding-bottom:2.5rem;padding-left:2.5rem\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:25%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-rounded\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" src=\"http:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/wa6E24A7_400x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5538\" srcset=\"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/wa6E24A7_400x400.jpg 400w, https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/wa6E24A7_400x400-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/wa6E24A7_400x400-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:75%\">\n<p><strong>Nicholas Loutrel<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Postdoc.<br><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"mailto:nicholas.loutrel@unimib.it\" target=\"_blank\">nicholas.loutrel@unimib.it<\/a><br><em>Stationary phaser, burst calculator, catastrophe theorizer. Still can&#8217;t understand why in Italy the entire country shuts down in August.<\/em><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns coblocks-author-columns has-background is-layout-flex wp-container-15 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"background-color:#8C8C