are-293x300.jpg 293w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 439px) 100vw, 439px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:75%\">\n<p><strong>Michele Mancarella<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Postdoc.<br><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"mailto:michele.mancarella@unimib.it\" target=\"_blank\">michele.mancarella@unimib.it<\/a><br><em>Cosmo perturber, Fisher matrixer, third generationer<\/em>. <em>Uses stats, machine learning, and theory to challenge Einstein\u2019s gravity. Curses in front of a python script, trains in a muay thai gym, cooks risotto.<\/em><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns coblocks-author-columns has-background is-layout-flex wp-container-21 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"background-color:#8C8C971A;padding-top:2.5rem;padding-right:2.5rem;padding-bottom:2.5rem;padding-left:2.5rem\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:25%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-rounded\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"http:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/costantino_square-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5062\" srcset=\"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/costantino_square-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/costantino_square-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/costantino_square-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/costantino_square-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/costantino_square.jpg 1499w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:75%\">\n<p><strong>Costantino Pacilio<\/strong><\/p>